# The repo-root .gitignore ignores every `lib/` directory (it is the Python
# packaging-artifacts pattern: build/, dist/, eggs/, lib/, lib64/, wheels/...).
# Re-include this app's TypeScript source `lib/` directory, which is real
# committed source, not a build artifact.
!/lib/
